snippet.title: Aquanox - Video Game Trailer (2001) PC Windows.
snippet.description:
Aquanox : official video game trailer. 
Developed by Massive Development GmbH
Published by Fishtank Interactive  in 2001 for PC (Windows). (Later relases published by Jowood as Fishtank closed in 2002).
Year : 2001
System : PC (Windows) 

Trailer found on the covermount CD of French 'Génération 4" Magazine (issue 145,  May 2001)
